---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — ZzzCalc"
  description="Privacy policy for ZzzCalc sleep cycle calculator. We do not collect, store, or share any personal data. Your sleep preferences stay on your device."
  canonical="https://zzzcalc.vercel.app/privacy"
>
  <Nav />

  <section class="pt-28 pb-16 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-24">
    <div class="container-main">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl tracking-tight mb-2" style="color: var(--text-page);">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xs mb-8" style="color: var(--text-muted);">Last updated: June 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-card-muted);">
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-lg sm:text-xl tracking-tight mb-3" style="color: var(--text-card);">1. What We Collect</h2>
            <p><strong style="color: var(--text-card);">We collect minimal, anonymized usage data through Google Analytics 4.</strong> This includes page views, session duration, approximate geographic region (country/city level), browser type, device type, and referring website. This information is aggregated and cannot be used to identify you personally. We use this data solely to understand how many people use the site and which features are most helpful.</p>
            <p class="mt-2">ZzzCalc does <em>not</em> collect your name, email address, or any sleep-related data you enter into the calculator.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-lg sm:text-xl tracking-tight mb-3" style="color: var(--text-card);">2. Local Storage</h2>
            <p>Your preferences — such as your selected wake time, sleep latency, and theme — are stored locally on your device using the browser's localStorage API. This data never leaves your computer or phone. You can clear it at any time by clearing your browser's site data.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-lg sm:text-xl tracking-tight mb-3" style="color: var(--text-card);">3. Cookies</h2>
            <p>ZzzCalc does not set its own cookies. However, <strong style="color: var(--text-card);">Google Analytics</strong> sets first-party cookies to distinguish unique users and throttle request rates. These cookies are anonymized and do not contain personally identifiable information. You can opt out of Google Analytics by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a>.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-lg sm:text-xl tracking-tight mb-3" style="color: var(--text-card);">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>ZzzCalc uses the following third-party services:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
              <li><strong style="color: var(--text-card);">Google Analytics</strong> — aggregated, anonymized usage statistics. Data is processed in accordance with <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Google's Privacy Policy</a>. IP addresses are anonymized before storage.</li>
              <li><strong style="color: var(--text-card);">Google Fonts</strong> — font files are loaded from Google's servers, which may log your IP address. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Google's Privacy Policy</a> for details.</li>
              <li><strong style="color: var(--text-card);">Vercel</strong> — the site is hosted on Vercel's platform. Vercel may collect standard server logs (request paths, timestamps, IP addresses) as part of their hosting infrastructure. See <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Vercel's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-2">We do <em>not</em> use advertising networks, social media widgets, tracking pixels, fingerprinting scripts, or any other data-collecting third-party services.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-lg sm:text-xl tracking-tight mb-3" style="color: var(--text-card);">5. Your Choices</h2>
            <p>You can opt out of Google Analytics at any time by:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
              <li>Installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a></li>
              <li>Enabling <strong style="color: var(--text-card);">Do Not Track</strong> in your browser settings</li>
              <li>Using a privacy-focused browser (Brave, Firefox with Enhanced Tracking Protection, etc.)</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-lg sm:text-xl tracking-tight mb-3" style="color: var(--text-card);">6. Open Source</h2>
            <p>ZzzCalc is open source under the GNU General Public License v3. The full source code is available on <a href="https://github.com/ankitv-dev/zzzcalc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-primary);">GitHub</a>. You are free to inspect, fork, and audit the code to verify these privacy claims.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-lg sm:text-xl tracking-tight mb-3" style="color: var(--text-card);">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>If this policy changes, the updated date at the top of this page will reflect the revision. Material changes will be noted in the project's commit history on GitHub.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-lg sm:text-xl tracking-tight mb-3" style="color: var(--text-card);">8. Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/ankitv-dev/zzzcalc/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-primary);">GitHub</a> or email <a href="mailto:ankit.kumar.verma.dev@gmail.com" style="color: var(--color-primary);">ankit.kumar.verma.dev@gmail.com</a>.</p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
